    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b style="color: lemonchiffon">Sand:</b> &#x2713; - Source spawining or item
      dropping is random. / X - One-Time drop only.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
      <b style="color: lightcoral">Red:</b> &#x2713; - Not recommended to farm this
      resource from this source. / X - Cannot drop from this source.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
